# Logos self-analysis store (coordinator quality bracket snapshots on main).
# The dev harness runs the pinned `logos` against this repo; its store/DB and
# derived state are ephemeral and never committed. See the dogfooding plan.
.logos/

# Binary-generated, version-stamped wiki skill — materialized locally by
# `logos wiki skill --emit` / `init -i` (FR-WK-08), regenerable, never tracked
# (unlike the hand-authored dev-process skills in .agents/skills/).
.agents/skills/logos-wiki/

# Local-only agent/harness config — kept out of version control per
# working-directory preference (make them local to this checkout).
.agents/
.claude/

# Rust build artefacts
/target/
.playwright-mcp/

# Local dev-tooling — kept out of the public release, retained on the maintainer's
